Cache actions provides rules actions for clearing drupal caches.

It currently supports clearing:

* Drupal cache bins
* CSS/JS cache
* The cache of specific views
* The cache of specific panel pages
* The cache of specific mini panels

Support for panel nodes are coming =)

This module is currently under review here: 

http://drupal.org/node/748850

If you like the idea, then please go there and submit a review.
